data.title: Tellico/DefaultFields
data.text:
This list is useful if you need to write or modify XSLT filters. Tellico's XSLT files use these names for processing data sources. Fields are defined in Tellico DTD (look for tellico.dtd file on your computer). But some filters add more fields.

In all collections

Internal name Public name Category id ID # of the entry Personal title Title General cdate Date Created Personal mdate Date Modified Personal

For books, bibliography and comics

Fields set in collection data definition

Bibliographic fields are named as BibteX default.

[abc] for generic services.

XMP is a proprietary meta-data format created by Adobe. See http://jabref.sourceforge.net/help/XMPHelp.php for its use in bibliography.
